Package: grattantheme
Type: Package
Title: Create Graphs In The Grattan Institute Style
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: person("Matt", "Cowgill", email = "matthew.cowgill@grattaninstitute.edu.au", 
                role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package enables the user to create ggplot2 charts that conform to the Grattan Institute style guide. It includes
    theme_grattan(), a ggplot2 theme with style guide-consistent defaults, as well as grattan_save(), a convenient way to save ggplot2
    charts in the correct size and resolution for use in Grattan reports. The colours from the Grattan palette are defined.
License: CC0
Imports:
    ggplot2
Depends:
    ggthemes
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
